<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Rent A Car</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/tw.build.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/animatedBackground.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/footer.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/about.css">
    <link rel="preload" as="image" href="/images/luxury-showroom-about.jpg">
    <link
    rel="stylesheet"
    href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css"
    integrity="sha512-DTOQO9RWCH3ppGqcWaEA1BIZOC6xxalwEsw9c2QQeAIftl+Vegovlnee1c9QX4TctnWMn13TZye+giMm8e2LwA=="
    crossorigin="anonymous"
    referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
  />
</head>
<body class="about-page">
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <section class="about-hero">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>About Rent A Car</h1>
            <p>Your premier destination for luxury and sport vehicle rentals</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About Content -->
    <section class="about-content">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="about-grid">
                <div class="about-text">
                    <h2>Our Journey</h2>
                    <p>Since 2015, we've been more than just a car rental service. We're curators of extraordinary automotive experiences, connecting passionate drivers with world-class vehicles. From weekend getaways to special celebrations, we make every mile memorable.</p>
                    
                    <h3>What Sets Us Apart?</h3>
                    <ul class="features-list">
                        <li><i class="fas fa-crown"></i> Exclusive access to luxury & exotic vehicles</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-headset"></i> Personal concierge service available 24/7</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-clock"></i> Flexible booking from hours to months</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-tools"></i> Meticulously maintained by certified technicians</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-handshake"></i> Transparent pricing with no hidden fees</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> Comprehensive insurance coverage included</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div class="stats-section">
                    <h2>Our Numbers</h2>
                    <div class="stats-grid">
                        <div class="stat-card">
                            <i class="fas fa-car"></i>
                            <span class="stat-number">25+</span>
                            <span class="stat-label">Premium Vehicles</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-card">
                            <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                            <span class="stat-number">1000+</span>
                            <span class="stat-label">Happy Customers</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-card">
                            <i class="fas fa-calendar"></i>
                            <span class="stat-number">8+</span>
                            <span class="stat-label">Years Experience</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-card">
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            <span class="stat-number">5.0</span>
                            <span class="stat-label">Average Rating</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Mission Section -->
    <section class="mission-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="mission-content">
                <h2>Driving Dreams Forward</h2>
                <p>We exist to turn automotive dreams into reality. Every vehicle in our collection tells a story of engineering excellence, and every rental is an opportunity to create unforgettable memories. Whether it's the roar of a supercar engine or the whisper-quiet luxury of a premium sedan, we deliver experiences that go beyond transportation.</p>
                
                <div class="values-grid">
                    <div class="value-card">
                        <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                        <h3>Safety First</h3>
                        <p>Every vehicle undergoes rigorous safety inspections and premium maintenance protocols to ensure your peace of mind on every journey</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="value-card">
                        <i class="fas fa-heart"></i>
                        <h3>Passion Driven</h3>
                        <p>We're automotive enthusiasts serving fellow car lovers. Our team understands what makes each drive special and memorable</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="value-card">
                        <i class="fas fa-gem"></i>
                        <h3>Uncompromising Quality</h3>
                        <p>From vehicle selection to customer service, we never settle for good enough. Excellence is our standard, not our goal</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    <script src="/js/mobileNav.js"></script>
</body>
</html>